   Artifex distributes Ghostscript / GhostPDL under the GNU Affero General
   Public License, version 3 or later, or under a separate commercial
   license. If you distribute or use a Ghostscript-enabled build of this
   package, you must comply with the Ghostscript licensing terms that apply
   to your use case.

   Official licensing references:

   - https://artifex.com/licensing
   - https://ghostscript.com/faq/

Effective package expression

Because this published package includes both Apache-2.0 package code and
AGPL-governed Ghostscript artifacts, the package manifest declares:

    (Apache-2.0 AND AGPL-3.0-or-later)

If you need Apache-only distribution terms, do not distribute a build that
includes the bundled Ghostscript artifacts.
